Package com.kissair.tags

This package contains the web application Tag classes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FlightAircraftTag
    The FlightAircraftTag class, whose purpose is to format aircraft info for usage in jsp pages.
    FlightArrLocTag
    The FlightArrLocTag class, whose purpose is to format flight arrival location info for usage in jsp.
    FlightArrTimestampTag
    The FlightArrTimestampTag class, whose purpose is to format flight arrival date and time for usage in jsp.
    FlightDepLocTag
    The FlightDepLocTag class, whose purpose is to format flight departure info for usage in jsp.
    FlightDepTimestampTag
    The FlightDepTimestampTag class, whose purpose is to format flight departure date and time for usage in jsp.
